     recognizing Haskell syntactical constructs.  It is based on a
     recursive descent Haskell parser.  â€˜TABâ€™ selects the next potential
     indentation position, â€˜S-TABâ€™ selects the previous one.  If a block
     is selected you can use â€˜TABâ€™ to indent the block more and â€˜S-TABâ€™
     to indent the block less.

     When â€˜electric-indent-modeâ€™ is enabled or the variable
