     decision table.  Sadly it is no longer developed and does not
     recognize newer Haskell syntax.  â€˜TABâ€™ cycles through all available
     indentation positions.

     To use â€˜haskell-indent-modeâ€™, add this to your â€˜~/.emacsâ€™ file:

